• Configs/config.application.credentials.json   => Only if structure changed
• Script/*.jsc                                  => Only when package is done
• CSS                                           => Only when package is done (conflict with LESS files)


Commandes :

find . -name "*.jsc" | xargs git update-index --assume-unchanged
find . -name "*.jsc" | xargs git update-index --no-assume-unchanged